detail.name: Son Gohan : Adolescence
detail.effect: [On Play] If you have 7 or fewer cards in your hand, choose up to 2 of your opponent's Battle Cards with costs of 3 or less and place them at the bottom of their owner's deck.

detail.name: 孫悟飯：青年期
detail.traits: サイヤ人/地球人/サタンシティ
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分の手札が7枚以下の場合、相手のコスト3以下のバトルカード2枚までを選び、デッキの下に置く。

faq.question: If you use this card's [On Play] skill to choose 2 of your opponent's Battle Cards, which player chooses the order that the cards are placed at the bottom of their owner's deck?
faq.answer: The owner (the person who constructed the deck that card is included in) of the card to be placed at the bottom of their deck chooses.

faq.question: このカードの【登場時】で相手のバトルカード2枚を選んだ場合、デッキの下に置く順番はどちらのプレイヤーが決めますか？
faq.answer: デッキの下に置かれるカードのオーナー（そのカードのデッキ構築時の所有者）です。
